The full source code is available at &lt;a href="http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/8c773cbf612c07e9061d1702f72d5c3cc2d116e6718d445ef03794a3e5e9e78d/http%3A//code.google.com/p/ietab/" rel="nofollow"&gt;http://code.google.com/p/ietab/&lt;/a&gt;.</description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">PCMan</dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2013 15:16:58 -0700</pubDate><guid>https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ie-tab/versions/4.0.20130422</guid></item><item><title>Nightly Tester Tools 3.7</title><link>https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/nightly-tester-tools/</link><description>&lt;em&gt;Note: To report feedback on compatibility to extension authors, use the &lt;a href="https://addons.mozilla.org/addon/add-on-compatibility-reporter/" rel="nofollow"&gt;Addon Compatibility Reporter&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/em&gt;

This extension adds a few extras useful to those that regularly test nightly builds of Firefox, Thunderbird, Seamonkey, and Songbird.

The following is a brief list of the extension's features:
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Titlebar customization&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Build ID retrieval&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Copy list of extensions to clipboard&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Screenshots&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Open profile folder&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Test crashing&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Disable addon compatibility checking (since 2.5, see Developer Comments)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;View pushlog of changes since last nightly&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
